platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: The Montessori education method was conceptualized at the start of the 20th century by an Italian pediatrician of the same name. The idea behind it is to offer children an education based on a sensory and kinetic way of learning. Montessori Preschool is based on this ideology and provides a variety of activities, which seek to guide children ages 3–7 as they embark on their first steps in the world of education.
這個 App 採用以感官和動覺學習方式為本的流行教育方法，提供各種活動來指導 3 至 7 歲的兒童邁出校園生活的第一步。
这款 App 专为 3-7 岁儿童设计，基于发展儿童潜能的蒙特梭利教育理念，通过丰富的活动，让儿童调动全身的感官获取信息，培养自主学习能力和探索精神，引导他们迈出学校教育的第一步。

Inspired by the popular education method based on a sensory and kinetic way of learning, this app provides a variety of activities to guide children ages 3–7 as they embark on their first steps in the world of schooling.

En s’inspirant de la populaire méthode d’éducation basée sur un apprentissage cinétique et sensoriel, cette app fournit de multiples activités pour aider les enfants âgés de 3 à 7 ans à s’adapter au milieu scolaire.
這款 App 參考了以感官與動態學習為基礎的知名教育方法，為 3 至 7 歲的孩子提供多元活動，幫助他們踏出學習的第一步。
